You bastard...

110
00:07:50,650 --> 00:07:52,490
Gum-Gum...

111
00:07:52,490 --> 00:07:53,740
Wait, wait, wait!

112
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:57,580
Let's run while he's distracted!

113
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,490
Okay!

114
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,500
I'll get even with you!

115
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:17,640
Sorry about your first prize.

116
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:21,430
Leave him alone. We had no
chance against that tiger.

117
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:25,650
But that was my prize!
He can't just steal it!

118
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:29,650
Y-Y-You fool! Don't shake it!

119
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,910
--You little...!
--Stop, Luffy!

120
00:08:58,010 --> 00:09:00,890
Sabo! Pull us up now!

121
