I-I got it!

122
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,890
Sorry!

123
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:12,150
We're home finally! Let's just
go to bed on such a bad day

124
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:16,030
Go to bed on a bad day?

125
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:17,570
Oh, I'm starving!

126
00:09:17,570 --> 00:09:19,830
--It's your fault!
--Ouch!

127
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:26,250
But if someone steals the prize you
caught by yourself for the first time,

128
00:09:26,250 --> 00:09:28,560
I can see why someone would get angry.

129
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:32,960
--But it's reckless to fight such a big tiger...
--That's something you would do!

130
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,760
