138
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:35,110
Ace! Sabo! You guys gotta come
aboard my ship! Okay? Say yes!

139
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,650
That's so sudden!

140
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:40,200
We decided to leave it to the future.

141
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:44,740
