142
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:47,200
and you'll need my help, won't you?

143
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:51,330
You're the one who needs help, aren't you?

144
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:52,170
Yeah.

145
00:10:52,170 --> 00:10:53,340
No!

146
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,130
I'm gonna help you!

147
00:10:55,130 --> 00:10:59,170
You guys are welcome to come aboard my ship.

148
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:00,590
--No, my ship!
--No, my ship!

149
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:03,640
Then, this is not gonna work.

150
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,770
--Are you sure about it?
--Yeah.

151
00:11:06,770 --> 00:11:07,970
Sabo?

152
00:11:07,970 --> 00:11:11,350
I'm not gonna work for anyone. Forget it.

153
00:11:11,820 --> 00:11:14,160
Come on! It's gonna be fun!

154
00:11:15,730 --> 00:11:18,250
Oh yeah! How about this?

155
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:21,360
The one who beats the big
tiger can be the captain!

156
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:24,740
The big tiger? Are you serious?

157
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:28,750
The chances of you becoming
a captain are pretty low.

158
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:34,710
That's not true! None of us
can compete against him now!

159
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,590
--Good idea!
--Good idea!

160
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:38,260
Yeah! Let's do it!

161
00:11:38,260 --> 00:11:39,920
--Alright!
--Alright!

162
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:47,890
Are you ready?

163
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:52,020
Yeah!

164
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:55,230
We went through so much to
catch these. What a waste!

165
00:11:55,230 --> 00:11:59,650
Don't complain. We caught
these to use them as bait.

166
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,700
