as strong as the tiger.

173
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:41,820
We can't beat the tiger if we can't beat him.

174
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:46,910
I see! So he's perfect for practice.

175
00:12:47,450 --> 00:12:50,660
--I go first!
--That's not fair!

176
